FUNCTIONALITIES

ITERATION 1:

1. User Authentication
The user can log into the application as a consumer or admin and can also log out of the system. Depending on the role, the system will display the appropriate interface.

2. View Products
The consumer can view all available clothes in the store, including details such as name, category, price, and stock.


ITERATION 2:

3. Add Product to Cart
The consumer can select a product and add it to the shopping cart.

4. View Cart
The consumer can see all products added to the cart.

5. Modify Cart
The consumer can change the quantity of a product in the cart or remove a product from the cart.


ITERATION 3:

6. Place Order
The consumer can place an order with the products from the cart, and the stock will be updated.

7. Add Products to Stock
The admin can add new products to the stock, including name, category, details, and price.

8. Order Management
The admin receives notifications for new orders and can see who placed the order and what products were ordered.
